sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User/KOL
    participant FE as Frontend+SDK
    participant W as Walrus
    participant F as note_factory (Move)
    participant PM as PredictManager (per-note)
    participant P as predict + OracleSVI (shared)
    participant K as Keeper (anyone)

    U->>FE: pick template + params
    FE->>FE: pricing-engine payoff + Monte-Carlo
    FE->>W: store term sheet PDF + backtest CSV
    W-->>FE: blob_id
    FE->>F: mint PTB (params, blob_id, payment)
    F->>F: collect issuance fee -> fee_vault
    F->>PM: new() + deposit(principal)
    loop each leg (strike/expiry)
        F->>P: predict::mint(Predict, PM, OracleSVI, MarketKey, qty)
    end
    F->>F: NoteBase{manager_id, legs[], blob_id} ; leaderboard::register
    F-->>U: transfer Note + tx receipt + Walrus URL

    Note over P: ... time passes, oracle reaches settled ...
    K->>P: redeem_permissionless(each leg) -> settle into PM balance
    U->>F: claim(Note, PM)
    F->>F: assert expiry & oracle settled & owner & manager match
    F->>PM: withdraw(balance) -> Coin<DUSDC>
    F->>F: perf_fee -> fee_vault ; emit NoteSettled
    F-->>U: payout Coin to owner ; Note deleted
